# MissionMed twin workstation state and AI handoff paths must stay trackable
# without opening whole trees to secrets or local machine state.
!_AI_HANDOFFS/
_AI_HANDOFFS/**
!_AI_HANDOFFS/**/
!_AI_HANDOFFS/*.md
!_AI_HANDOFFS/**/*.md
!_SYSTEM_LOGS/
!_SYSTEM_LOGS/MM_ACTIVITY_LOG.md
!_SYSTEM_LOGS/LEARNINGS_LOG.jsonl
!08_AI_SYSTEM/
