!_SYSTEM/TWIN_STATE.md
!_SYSTEM/ACTIVE_WORK.md
!_SYSTEM/DUAL_MAC_SYNC_PROTOCOL.md
!_SYSTEM/mm-sync-start.sh
!_SYSTEM/mm-sync-end.sh

# Reassert sensitive ignores after safe unignore rules. Last match wins.
